me":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775106560831,"sessionId":"ef8c7010-42de-4d3d-87e8-cf65e2242964","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":49666,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/ef8c7010-42de-4d3d-87e8-cf65e2242964.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时任务的自主学习检测。我需要先查询 sessions_list 确认是否有活跃对话。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_itwi92twbl4d_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775106561414}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775106570290}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3f9609e","parentId":"20f8d19c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:09:39.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个session是当前cron任务自身的session，不是用户活跃对话。我需要查看是否有其他用户对话。session列表中只有一个session，就是当前这个cron任务。\n\n实际上，sessions_list返回的session只有一个，而这个是cron任务本身的session，不是真实用户对话。\n\n但从返回结果来看，updatedAt是最近的时间，这意味着这是当前正在运行的任务。我需要更仔细地判断——如果只有一个session且是cron自身的，那确实没有活跃对话。\n\n让我检查一下，返回的sessions数组中只有一个元素，这就是当前cron任务的session。所以没有真实用户活跃对话。\n\n我应该执行自主学习。但首先我需要读取技能文件 miaoda-web-search 来进行搜索。\n\n不过，我需要先读取技能文件。让我查看可用的skill。","thinkingSignature":"0c80a13b9da8193f727b5686541df403671f67f221cc6fa548cd1d1e9cc6913c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n检测到只有当前 cron 任务自身的 session，没有真实用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n\n先读取 web-search 技能文件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1int5aboij56_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":828,"output":215,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45024,"cost":{"input":0.00024839999999999997,"output":0.000258,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018258299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775106570296}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d623679","parentId":"e3f9609e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:09:39.306Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1int5aboij56_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775106579303}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ca9b811","parentId":"1d623679","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:09:45.171Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。让我进行搜索。","thinkingSignature":"2306a52cc4d26a810d19b5a8f245b7d6ac59e2e803c5d7a0d4a18c7b53ec1cd8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7p1pmk0km207_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7p1pmk0km207_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7p1pmk0km207_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务发展趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7p1pmk0km207_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 政企行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1558,"output":219,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45758,"cost":{"input":0.0004674,"output":0.0002628,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020496299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775106579306}}
